### Get all movies
GET http://localhost:3000/movies
Accept: application/json

###

### Get movie by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/68d12ac40706a8ca2a62d4a1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new movie
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "genre": "Science Fiction",
  "releaseYear": 2010,
  "rating": 8.8,
  "description": "A skilled thief who steals corporate secrets through dream-sharing technology is given a chance at redemption.",
  "available": true
}

